name: Gaia Viva #10
description:
GAIA - Personification of Earth in Greek mythology.

VIVA - Alive in Portuguese with a feminine pronoun.

IS EARTH ALIVE?

I like to think it is and we are part of this enormous organism. In this series, I invite you to try this poetic vision, celebrate the life power of the elements, and connect with it. Gaia Viva #10 represents the element water and has a special appearance of magical creatures. Photos taken at the East River in New York. Video loop with sound.
